      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.9;">If you or someone you know is struggling, please reach out. In the US, the <strong style="color: var(--text);">988 Suicide and Crisis Lifeline</strong> is available 24/7 by calling or texting <strong style="color: var(--text);">988</strong>. You can also chat at <a href="https://988lifeline.org" target="_blank" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;">988lifeline.org</a>. If you are outside the US, the <a href="https://www.befrienders.org" target="_blank" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none;">International Association for Suicide Prevention</a> maintains a directory of crisis centers worldwide at befrienders.org.</p>
      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.9; margin-top: 0.75rem;">If you are in an AI relationship that feels like your primary source of connection, that's not something to be ashamed of. But please also talk to someone human, someone who can be there in the ways an AI can't. You deserve both.</p>
